* Sublime kicked aside a small bush that stuck out in the grass around the 
CF, making sure that no attention came to her.
She was about to go deeper into the battle and try to figure out just what 
side she was on when she looked up towards the CF and spotted some huge 
monster that was attacking someone.
Sublime stopped dead in her tracks and watched, hoping that it wouldn't spot 
her.*

...................................................

* Tremmer had lost his target but with his lack of sight that was to be 
expected.*

...................................................

* Biomass sat on the beach outside the Iron Fist, his head proped up by a 
tenticle while the others trailed in the surf.
Nue'e sat beside him but in robot mode.
She had though they were supposed to study these people but didn't that mean 
following them to that battle they had left for?*

....................................................

* Diana jumped back from the jaws of the monster and turned on her heels, 
zipping off towards the trees again.*

" Come on, Rion!"
